metadata.name: Mirikinokis #2
metadata.description: 3333 CC0 Mirikinokis .The Mirikinokis are an ancestral clan of ninjas who protect the blockchain due to the rumor of the near arrival of their archenemies.... to be continued. Formed by different races, they will fight together to fulfill their mission. The skill of the Mirikinori is the art of winning.
